stories.text:
I recently read about Warp in https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=21070321.

Turns out there is a tool to get a wireguard profile easily: https://github.com/ViRb3/wgcf

How to create an account and connect:

wgcf register wgcf generate wg-quick up ./wgcf-profile.conf
